    <div data-cid="5614671">
        <div class="main review-item" id="5614671">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/princesspainter/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img9.doubanio.com/icon/u1299820-26.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/princesspainter/" class="name">逍遥地蔷薇~</a>

            <span class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>

        <span content="2012-10-12" class="main-meta">2012-10-12 16:41:11</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5614671/">一场群体无意识的浪漫主义行动</a></h2>

                <div id="review_5614671_short" class="review-short" data-rid="5614671">
                    <div class="short-content">

                              最近对清朝刑罚感兴趣，有人推荐了檀香刑。读了三天，昨晚才读完（并且中途看到钱雄飞被凌迟一段文后不得不去看了两集生活大爆炸来缓解心情）然后就传来了莫言已经刚刚获诺贝尔奖的消息。就依檀香刑来说，至少和村上春树比起来，莫言拿这个奖是够实力的。      这部小说...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5614671-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
